      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，两个功能分支的优先级或者显示顺序有要求吗？比如feature-1和feature-2谁在上面？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "feature-1",
        "feature-2",
        "order"
