    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "feature-1放上面，order设为0，feature-2在下面order为1。feature-2那边需要两个提交f和g，feature-1那边先空着，后面再补。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "feature-1 order: 0",
        "feature-2 order: 1",
        "commit f",
        "commit g"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，主分支commit a，然后分出两个分支，feature-2上做了f和g两个提交。现在feature-1是空的，需要我checkout过去做提交吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout",
        "feature-1",
        "commit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，切到feature-1做一个提交x。然后回到main分支，再做提交b，最后把feature-2合并进来。这样整个IoT控制器的迭代流程就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout feature-1",
        "commit x",
        "checkout main",
        "commit b",
        "merge feature-2"
